* 2 Inch open reel to reel analog video system<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://archive.totterslane.co.uk/tech/quad.htm |title=2 inch Quad tape |access-date=2021-07-14 |archive-date=2021-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210714213414/http://archive.totterslane.co.uk/tech/quad.htm }}</ref>
